<li id="cite_note-29"><b><a href="#cite_ref-29" title="">^</a></b> Two states, <a href="/wiki/Alaska" title="Alaska">Alaska</a> and <a href="/wiki/Vermont" title="Vermont">Vermont</a>, do not require a permit or license for carrying a concealed weapon to this day, following Kentucky's original position.</li>
